INSERT INTO `articles` (`id`, `title`, `meta_description`, `slug`, `image`, `content`, `date`, `lang`, `map`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `no_index`, `type`, `external_content`, `button_txt`, `button_link`, `expired`) VALUES
(1, 'Putting on a show at the fringe festival', NULL, 'putting-on-a-show-at-the-fringe-festival', 'https://assets.yvanzim.com/images/articles/coming-soon.jpg', '<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">For those who haven\'t had the chance of attending, the Edinburgh Fringe Festival (or \"The Fringe\") is the world\'s largest arts festival, taking place every August in the amazing city of Edinburgh. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">During that month, thousands of performances are staged in hundreds of venues across the city. In fact every conceivable space becomes a \"theater\", from auditoriums to corner pubs.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\"> In August 2023, there were 3535 registered shows with a total of 52000 scheduled performances. There is a lot going on! </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">Among all the others shows was: \"Tangled d\"Illusions\". A show I wrote and performed for a the whole month. It was an amazing experience. On paper it\'s an experience that only lasted one month, but in reality it\'s a much bigger commitment. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">I thought I\'d layout the process, from A to Z, of bringing a show to the Fringe. The goal is to make this article useful for performers and an interesting peek behind the curtains for non-performers&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h2><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-Bold&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:1}\">Applying to the fringe festival</span></h2>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">Before the actual show writing begins, there is a good be of leg work to do. </span><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">Performers need to decide where and when the show will de performed... send in an application... assemble a budget... and more.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">1. Free fringe or paid fringe? </span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">There is no one festival organiser. Instead, there are multiple small festival organisers. As a performer, you need to apply for a venue through one of these organisations. They\'re broadly split into two groups: </span></p>\n<h4><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Paid Fringe </span></h4>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">Shows at the paid fringe are ticketed. Prices range from 10-20pounds. However, performers are expected to pay for the venue. Prices vary depending on the room and the organisations. The big venues (The \"big four\") are <a href=\"https://gildedballoon.co.uk\">The Guild Balloon</a>, <a href=\"https://assemblyfestival.com/\">Assembly Hall</a>, <a href=\"https://underbelly.co.uk/festival/underbelly-at-the-edinburgh-fringe\">Underbelly</a> and the <a href=\"https://www.pleasance.co.uk/events/location/Edinburgh\">Pleasance.</a></span></p>\n<p>The prices they charge for venues vary widly. It can be anywhere from &pound;2,000 for the month up too &pound;10,000+ pounds for a week.&nbsp;</p>\n<h4><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Free fringe </span></h4>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">Shows at free fringe are non-ticketed. Spectator\'s are generally asked for a donnation at the end. However, the performer get\'s the room for free. </span><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">The <a href=\"https://freefringe.org.uk/about-us/\">PBH Free Fringe</a> were the first to introduce this model. They were joined a few years later by the <a href=\"https://freefestival.co.uk/\">Laughing Horse Free Festival</a>. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">Whether or not an event is ticketed has nothing to do with the quality of a show. It can be excellent (or terrible) regardless if you you paid to get in. It\'s just a different business model for the performer/organisers. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">For a first show at the fringe, it\'s generally recommended to go with the Free Fringe. Advice I heeded and I\'m glad I did. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:102,&quot;startingListItemNumber&quot;:2}}\">2. Choosing perfoming dates </span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">In 2023 the fringe was from the 4th to the 28 of August 2023. If possible, it\'s recommended to do the \"full run\". All 26 shows with maybe a day off or two. For example, I did 25 shows and took one day off.</span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">Shorter runs (for example a week) are less likely to be scheduled.&nbsp; Their is a lot more demand for them and they they</span><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\"> make sechduling a nightmare. For that reason, full runs generally get priority. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">The good news is that it\'s easier to fincially make a show work if you\'re performing more shows. And in any case, if you\'ve made it all the way to Edinbrugh, you might as well make the most of it! </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:102,&quot;startingListItemNumber&quot;:2}}\">3. Submiting an application </span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">The one thing performers hate the most... paperwork. But their is no way around it. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">Applications are similar from one festival to another. They ask you about your performer &ldquo;CV&rdquo; and as much information as you can give about the show you hope to put on. When I sent my application in, my show wasn\'t fully established. I mostly had an outline. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">Applications for the fringe open in October and, depending on the organisations, stay open until May(ish). Generally organisers start assigning veues late January. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">Everyone recommends sending an application in as early as possible. Personally, I\'m not sure it makes a huge difference. I sent my application in late November but only got a reply in May. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:102,&quot;startingListItemNumber&quot;:3}}\">4. Getting a venue </span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">Most shows take place in the \"old town\" (around Edinbrough University) however, the \"new town\" (around George Street) is has a lot of offer too. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">I was offered a spot in a venue I hadn\'t originally considered (The Eastside). This turned out to be great for a few reasons: </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:101}}\">It\'s accross from the Assembly Room so people were nearby which was helpful for flyering.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:101}}\">They setup a food court right outside of the Eastside. Again, this was really helpful for flyering. </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:101}}\">Lastly, the staff in the Eastside were great. I only have good things to say about them. That really made my fringe experience fun.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:101}}\">The room itself was called The Lounge. It was technically a 60seat room but at 55 it was already getting cosy. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:102,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1,&quot;startingListItemNumber&quot;:3}}\">5. Budgeting </span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">This is the scary part of putting on a fringe show. There are no official statistics but it&rsquo;s fairly clear that most shows loose money. Especially first time performers. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">By far the biggest expense at the fringe is housing. It&rsquo;s definitely insane. Edinbrugh housing problem is well documented. At the Fringe is partly responsible for this crisis. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">All in putting on the show cost me around 5000euros </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">// include breakdown //</span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">- Venue </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">- Housing&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">- Food&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">- Equipment&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h2><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-Bold&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:1}\">Assembling a show </span></h2>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4}}\">When writting a show, there is something facinating (and terrifying) about starting with a blank page and turning it into a show. It\'s a</span><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4},&quot;fontHints&quot;:0}\"> lot of work. Fortunately, it&rsquo;s fun work. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Past experiences</span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;fontHints&quot;:0}\">In Dublin, I was part of a magic Trio called Mind Feck. For almost 4 years, we performed a monthly show at the Clockwork door. Through these shows, I developed a taste for material I like / material that suits me.</span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;fontHints&quot;:0}\">// Mind feck picture&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">The script </span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;fontHints&quot;:0}\">In December, after sending my application in, I compiled an outline of the show. In January, I worked on it with my friend and director. We streamlined my outline and determined which areas needed to be explored further. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Assembling the material</span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;fontHints&quot;:0}\">Once in France, I started assembling the material for the show. This is intense work for a magic show,. It&rsquo;s everything from which shirt to wear on stage, to which pens will be used during the show. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;fontHints&quot;:0}\">It\'s is a balancing act. You want the show to be as great as possible but you have a budget to meet &amp; everything needs to fit in a suit case</span><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">. </span><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">For example, instead of a nice wooden table, maybe a flimsily light weight metallic one it better. </span><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;fontHints&quot;:0}\"> For big productions, producers are in charge of this. But for the fringe you&rsquo;re on your own. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Building the act</span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;fontHints&quot;:0}\">The next step after gathering everything is building the act. This applies to both the set desgin and the actual tricks which were all being created from scratch for the show. I was mostly done by June but It realistic I kept tweaking things until the start of the fringe. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Rehersing the act</span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">Once the show was assembled, I started rehersing it end-from-end. I realistically started doing this late June. I find the process enjoyable but very demanding. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">If I was to do it again, the only thing I would change is emphasising is emphasises more on rehearsing with the tech (The microphone and the music). That caused problems early on in the fringe. </span></p>\n<h2><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-Bold&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:1}\">Marketing</span> <span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-Bold&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:1}\">a fringe</span> <span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-Bold&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:1}\">show</span></h2>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">\"Build it and the will come\" is the worst saying in the world. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">At least in regards to putting on a show. Being proactive about marketing is critical to the success of the show. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">I was very fortunate to be sold-out or full almost every day. It\'s not a given. You do hear some horror stories. It\'s often said that the average attendance at the Free Fringe is 3 or 4 spectators per show. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">The last thing you want is to show-up and not be able to perform because your room is empty. That was something I was very worried about. I put in a good amount of work for promoting the show before I even got there. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">There are many moving parts to promoting a show. I won\'t go through everything here but few of the things that worked well for me were: </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Branding a show</span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">The the branding of the show (the deisgn, the artwork, the ads copy...). I had a vision of what I wanted and everything came together really well. During the month multiple people told me they had walked in simply because they liked the ad copy or the design. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Getting Posters</span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">Getting posters made and hung up can be very expensive and it\'s hard to stand out as the city is covered with posters. For that reason it\'s a bit of a gamble. However it really paid off for my shows. </span></p>\n<p>// include picture</p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Guest spots</span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">There many (many) shows at the fringe who are looking for and/or happy to take on guest acts. These are usually 10minute spots. At the end of the show, you can hand out flyers for your own-show. They\'re extremly fun as It\'s a change to hang out with other performers. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">The catch is that its requires a lot of planning ahread of time. You need to look through all of the existing shows, find the ones that are a good match, and reach out to the organisers asked if they accept guest performers. I did 25 during the month. An average of one a day. </span></p>\n<h2><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-Bold&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:1}\">Performing at the fringe festival </span></h2>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">You\'ve got the room. You built the show. Now it\'s time to hit the road and perform! My preview show was on the 3rd of august. And then I was on every day until the 28th. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Commuting </span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">I was really lucky with the housing arrangments. I\'d leave around 9:30 and I was about 30min away from my venue. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Preparing the room</span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">Everyday, I\'d get to the venue around 10:00 and I had about an hour of preperation to get the space show-ready. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">As I was the first show of the day I needed get the room opperation. For example get the chairs/stools in line. Make sure the equipment was ready and on. That took about 30min. Then I had to get my get my owen gear ready. For example, getting the table out, plug my sound equipment in, set the stage and so on. Again this took about 30min. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Flyering </span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">My goal was to be out flyering by 11:00 everyday. I was fairly consistant. I would flyer from 11:00 to around 12:20-12:30 everyday. I also hired someone to help me flyer. He was there every day from 11:30 to 12:30. // Tag Lenny </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">That was a combined 2:30 hours of flyers a day. That seemed to be just right to ill my room 60 seat room. Exhausting but definitly effective. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">The amount of flyering required to fill a room depends on the show, the location and the timeslot. I was on during lunch time, which was a bit of a pain, but on the otherhand I had very little compeitition on at the same time. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Show time </span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">At 12:30 I would open the doors and get people in. The show would then kick-off at 12:40. The show itself was written to be 50-55minutes. If I finished around 13:30 that was ideal. The room would be \"empty\" around 13:40. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Cleaning the room </span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">The Fringe festival is on a very tight schedule. I only had 15min to clean the room and be out before the next act started getting his spectators in. The show is (purposfully) a bit of a mess which made this a bit of a rush. Once back stage I would do some more cleaning. I\'d usually be out of the venue by 2:00. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Flyering </span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">I would occasionally flyer again for an hour (give or take) to promote the show next day. I would mostly do this if I their was rain forcasted the next day... let\'s not this forget this Soctoland. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Getting the next show ready </span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">This part of the schedule had a bit more wiggle room. Between the commute back and my late lunch it varied day to day. But I had approximatly 1:30 of set-up time to tommorow\'s show. I would usually be done around 18:00. </span></p>\n<h3><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3},&quot;font&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SFUIText-LightItalic&quot;,&quot;pointSize&quot;:0},&quot;fontHints&quot;:2}\">Guest spots</span></h3>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">Almost every evening I had one or two guest spots. There are 10minute performances you do as part of other shows. This would allow me to exit flyer to promote my own show. I would be on anytime between 8:00 and 1:00am. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3}}\">A few of my highlights were performing at the Late night magic show, hosted by Tom Brace. It\'s always fun seing what other magicians are up too. The Doing Bits cabaret hosted by Tom // get name which was always briliant. Lastly the Midnight cabaret hosted by ///. Late night entertainment at Edinburgh is hilariously crazy and now has a special place in my heart. </span></p>\n<h2><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;fontHints&quot;:1}\">That&rsquo;s a wrap </span></h2>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;fontHints&quot;:0}\">One of the questions I get asked the most is: would I go back? Definitely. It was hard work, but I&rsquo;ve rarely had so much fun in a month. </span></p>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1},&quot;fontHints&quot;:0}\">The catch is that logistics are intense. Performers who go year-in year-out plan their year (and business model) specifically around the fringe. Because of that, going back isn\'t not on my immediate radar. However, I do hope to go back one day! </span></p>\n<h2><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">A few thank you </span></h2>\n<p><span data-tt=\"{&quot;paragraphStyle&quot;:{&quot;alignment&quot;:4,&quot;style&quot;:3,&quot;writingDirection&quot;:1}}\">Firstly, thanks to the Laughing Horse Free Festival who gave me a spot in the schedule and thanks to the staff at the Eastside for making the month more fun. I\'d also like to thank Luke Osey, The performing Nerd and Ian Kendall who gave me loads of advice when preping for the fringe. Thanks to Brian Daly who helped with the staging and construction of the show. Lastly thanks to my wife who helped me throughout and tolerated me</span></p>', '2024-04-04', 'en', NULL, '2024-04-04 09:42:02', '2024-07-23 11:30:32', 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2, 'Tangled D\'Illusions | Edinburgh Fringe', NULL, 'fringe-tangled-illusions', 'https://assets.yvanzim.com/images/pages/fringe/yvan-zim-fringe.jpg', '<p>What happens when you mix a Franco-Irish magician with a lot of spare time and inflated sense of self? Tangled d\'Illusions. This year, world-class trickster Yvan Zim brings his new show to the Fringe. Be prepared for a captivating mix of mind-reading, comedy, escapes and real magic. With his quick wit, comedic charm and sleight of hand, he will keep you on the edge of your seat!</p>\n<p><strong>Dates</strong>: 3-28th of August 2023<br /><strong>Time</strong>: 12:40pm <br /><strong>Location</strong>: Eastside&nbsp; - The Lounge<br /><strong>Price</strong>: PWYC</p>', '2023-07-31', 'en', NULL, '2024-08-06 14:00:16', '2024-09-07 09:39:03', 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(3, 'Soirée de Lancement du Hyundai TUCSON', NULL, 'lancement-hyundai-tucson', 'https://assets.yvanzim.com/images/articles/hyundai-cover-image.png', '<p>Je me deplace <a href=\"../../fr/magicien-a-vichy\">regulierement a Vichy</a> pour des spectacles de magie. Au mois de Juin, j\'ai l\'occasion de faire une soir&eacute;e un peu differente!</p>\n<p>J\'ai &eacute;t&eacute; invit&eacute; a performer a la soir&eacute;e de lancement du nouveau Hyundai TUCSON. L\'equipe &agrave; fait Hyundai montage pour resumer l\'evenment.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/share/r/yJ8yMewVtuHkW2Cz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://assets.yvanzim.com/images/articles/hyundai-video-image.png\" alt=\"Facebook hyundai video\" width=\"704\" height=\"526\" /></a></p>\n<p>Un grand merci &agrave; Hyundai pour m\'avoir invit&eacute; &agrave; participer &agrave; cet &eacute;v&eacute;nement m&eacute;morable. Et restez &agrave; l\'aff&ucirc;t de leurs prochains &eacute;v&eacute;nements &mdash; je suis s&ucirc;r qu\'ils seront tout aussi magiques !</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2024-06-22', 'fr', NULL, '2024-08-27 06:28:09', '2024-08-27 06:45:29', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(4, '3nvoutement', NULL, 'nouveau-project-3nvoutement', 'https://assets.yvanzim.com/images/articles/3nvoutement-header.png', '<p>Un nouveau project ce lance: <strong><a href=\"https://3nvoutement.com/\">3nvoutement</a></strong></p>\n<p>C\'est un spectacle que je monte avec deux bons amis. Le concept est simple, bien que la r&eacute;alisation ne le soit pas : partager 3 univers en 1 spectacle.</p>\n<h3>Maxime Jury- <strong>Hypnotiseur </strong></h3>\n<p>Maxime, praticien dipl&ocirc;m&eacute; en hypnose ericksonienne, va envo&ucirc;ter votre public et lui faire vivre une exp&eacute;rience dont il se souviendra... m&ecirc;me apr&egrave;s s\'&ecirc;tre fait r&eacute;veiller.</p>\n<h3>Diego Ibars - <strong>Mentaliste </strong></h3>\n<p>Les limites du possible sont elles celles que vous imaginez ? Diego combine ses connaissances en psychologie, divination et anciennes civilisations pour cr&eacute;er des exp&eacute;riences de lecture de l\'esprit.</p>\n<h3>Yvan Zim - <strong>Magicien </strong></h3>\n<p>Avec plus de 10 ans d\'exp&eacute;rience en tant que magicien professionnel, Yvan Zim sait s\'adapter &agrave; son audience avec humour et savoir-faire pour offrir au spectacteurs une exp&eacute;rience de magie inoubliable</p>', '2024-08-31', 'fr', NULL, '2024-09-03 14:38:09', '2024-09-07 09:44:01', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5, 'Illusions Clandestines', NULL, 'illusions-clandestines-lyon', 'https://assets.yvanzim.com/images/articles/coming-soon.jpg', '<div class=\"text-white my-4\"><em>Illusions Clandestines, c\'est une soir&eacute;e magique et intimiste unique &agrave; Lyon. Au plus pr&egrave;s des artistes, vivez une soir&eacute;e berc&eacute;e d\'illusions, &agrave; l\'ambiance tamis&eacute;e et d&eacute;tendue. 4 Artistes se succ&egrave;dent afin de vous faire plonger dans leur univers magique.</em></div>\n<div class=\"text-white my-4\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"text-white my-4\">Les spectacles ont lieu une fois par mois a Lyon (hors vacance d\'&eacute;te). Le format du spectacle est inspir&eacute; des speakeasy americians (Les cab&eacute;rets clandestins des ann&eacute;e 1920-1930)... donc toutes l\'organisation est secrete.&nbsp;L\'adresse exacte et le nom des artistes vous serons communiqu&eacute;e par sms 24h avant le spectacle.</div>\n<div class=\"text-white my-4\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"text-white my-4\">Si c\'est quelque chose qui vous intrigue, n\'hestiez pas a m\'envoyer un message!&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"text-white my-4\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"text-white my-4\">&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"text-yellow-600 border border-yellow-600 p-4 text-center\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2024-09-03', 'fr', NULL, '2024-09-03 14:43:07', '2024-09-03 14:53:28', 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(6, 'Mind Feck: It\'s a wrap', 'Dublin\'s Magic Trio', 'mind-feck-it-a-wrap', 'https://assets.yvanzim.com/images/articles/mind-feck-header.jpg', '<div>\n<p><em><strong>Mind Feck: Dublin\'s Maddest Magic Show</strong></em></p>\n<p><em>Prepare for your mind to be fecked. Dublin\'s magic trio will beguile and mesmerize you with trickery and illusions like you\'ve never seen before! There will be cardistry, mentalism, sleight of hand, devilishly quick wit, and lots more.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>In 2017, along with two of my good friends, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/connmcmagic/?hl=en\">Conn McCormack</a> and <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/oisinfoleymindreader/\">Oisin Foley</a>, we performed a &ldquo;one-off&rdquo; magic show at <a href=\"https://www.clockworkdoor.ie\">the Clockwork Door</a> in Dublin. Little did we know that Mind Feck was born!</p>\n<p>As magicians, we mostly work solo, so getting the opportunity to work with other magicians is always a blast.</p>\n<p>This &ldquo;one-off&rdquo; performance quickly turned into a monthly show. At the time, we were the only regular magic show in Dublin! Every month, the three of us would try out new tricks and ideas on stage. In fact, many of the effects in my show Tangled D\'Illusions were born while performing Mind Feck.</p>\n<p>Over time, we tweaked things. We improved the format, the timing, the content&hellip; and slowly turned the show into a really fun night out for the audiences (biased opinion?).</p>\n<p>Sadly, all good things come to an end. In 2023, I moved from Dublin to Lyon, France. Although I&rsquo;m sure we&rsquo;ll one day get to share a stage again, for now, we&rsquo;ve had to bring down the curtains on Mind Feck.</p>\n<p>It\'s been a really fun adventure and one which I cherish.</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://assets.yvanzim.com/images/articles/mind-feck-performance.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"723\" height=\"506\" /></p>\n</div>', '2023-11-10', 'en', NULL, '2024-09-03 14:53:32', '2024-09-09 15:13:25', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(7, 'Tangled D\'Illusions | Dublin', NULL, 'tangled-illusions-dublin-0924', 'https://assets.yvanzim.com/images/pages/fringe/yvan-zim-fringe.jpg', '<p>What happens when you mix a Franco-Irish magician with a lot of spare time and inflated sense of self? Tangled d\'Illusions. This year, world-class trickster Yvan Zim brings his new show to the Clockwork Door in Dublin. Be prepared for a captivating mix of mind-reading, comedy, escapes and real magic. With his quick wit, comedic charm and sleight of hand, he will keep you on the edge of your seat!</p>\n<p><strong>Date</strong>: 26th of September 2023<br /><strong>Doors open</strong>: 8:00 PM<br /><strong>Show Time</strong>: 8:30 PM<br /><strong>Location</strong>: The Clockwork Door, <em>51 Wellington Quay, Temple Bar, Dublin, D02 NH04</em><br /><strong>Price</strong>: &euro;12:00</p>', '2024-09-09', 'en', NULL, '2024-09-09 15:14:30', '2024-09-09 15:28:20', 0, 1, NULL, 'Buy Tickets', 'https://www.eventbrite.ie/e/tangled-dillusions-a-magic-show-like-no-other-tickets-1006706505257', 1),
(8, 'Le Délire des Illusions | 2024', 'Préparez-vous à un mélange captivant de mentalisme, de comédie, d\'évasions et de magie contemporaine', 'lyon-2024-le-delire-des-illusions', 'https://assets.yvanzim.com/images/pages/fringe/yvan-zim-fringe.jpg', '<p>Que se passe t-il lorsqu\'un magicien franco-irlandais se retrouve avec beaucoup de temps libre et un &eacute;go surdimensionn&eacute; ?</p>\n<div id=\"speDescription\">Dans ce nouveau spectacle de 60 minutes, le tricheur, mystificateur et magicien Yvan Zim explore avec humour les nombreuses facettes de la perception de soi.<br /><br />Pr&eacute;parez-vous &agrave; un m&eacute;lange captivant de mentalisme, de com&eacute;die, d\'&eacute;vasions et de magie contemporaine alors qu\'Yvan Zim explore, d&eacute;compose et examine comment l\'on en vient &agrave; se d&eacute;finir au travers des m&eacute;tiers, des passions, des langues et autres faux-semblants...<br /><br />De part son esprit vif, son charme comique et sa dext&eacute;rit&eacute;, Yvan Zim vous tiendra en haleine et vous fera remettre en question le champ des possibles.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><strong>Dates</strong>: Samedi &agrave; 17:00, Oct-Nov 2024<br /><strong>Lieu</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.lerepairedelacomedie.com\">Le Repaire de la Com&eacute;die</a>, <a tabindex=\"0\" href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x47f4eafe7bd3cde7:0xbc6e582dc223efe0?sa=X&amp;ved=1t:8290&amp;ictx=111\" data-url=\"/maps/place//data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x47f4eafe7bd3cde7:0xbc6e582dc223efe0?sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjjj4HNy9iIAxWJQUEAHf_aGPwQ4kB6BAgKEAA\">2 Pl. des Capucins, 69001 Lyon, France</a><br /><strong>Billet</strong>: &euro;15:00</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', '2024-09-23', 'fr', NULL, '2024-09-23 07:54:20', '2025-02-04 10:38:58', 0, 1, NULL, 'Réservations', 'https://www.billetreduc.com/356358/evt.htm', 1),
(9, 'Esprit Mariage : Réseau des Professionnels du Mariage', NULL, 'esprit-mariage-2025', 'https://assets.yvanzim.com/images/articles/esprit_mariage_cover.png', '<p data-pm-slice=\"1 3 []\">En 2023, j\'ai rejoint Esprit Mariage, un r&eacute;seau de professionnels du mariage. Si vous pr&eacute;parez votre mariage et cherchez des prestataires de confiance dans la Loire, c\'est une ressource incontournable !</p>\n<h3>Une Communaut&eacute; de Passionn&eacute;s</h3>\n<p>Esprit Mariage est une communaut&eacute; qui r&eacute;unit <strong>plus de 70 professionnels</strong> s&eacute;lectionn&eacute;s pour leur expertise et leur savoir-faire. L\'objectif est simple : vous offrir des services de qualit&eacute; pour que votre mariage soit &agrave; la hauteur de vos r&ecirc;ves.</p>\n<p>Le r&eacute;seau est aujourd\'hui dirig&eacute; par Marine Curtil, consultante en &eacute;v&eacute;nementiel. Elle g&egrave;re &eacute;galement l\'organisation du Festival Esprit Mariage, un &eacute;v&eacute;nement phare pour les futurs mari&eacute;s.</p>\n<h3>Comment Profiter du R&eacute;seau ?</h3>\n<ul data-spread=\"false\">\n<li>\n<p>Consultez la liste des partenaires sur le site internet Esprit Mariage.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>D&eacute;couvrez le carnet d\'adresses disponible chez les adh&eacute;rents.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Participez au Festival Esprit Mariage pour rencontrer les professionnels en personne.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Festival Esprit Mariage 2025</h3>\n<p>Chaque ann&eacute;e, Esprit Mariage organise un salon du mariage &agrave; Saint-&Eacute;tienne. C\'est un rendez-vous incontournable pour les futurs mari&eacute;s ! Cette ann&eacute;e, retrouvez-nous les <strong>22 &amp; 23 mars 2025</strong> &agrave; <a href=\"https://saint-etienne.lafabuleusecantine.fr/?_gl=1%2As2f4vh%2A_gcl_au%2ANTYzODY0MTc4LjE3Mzg2NTkzMjE.%2A_ga%2AOTYwNjQ2NjcyLjE3Mzg2NTkzMjE.%2A_ga_LY5VJX6935%2AMTczODY1OTMyMC4xLjAuMTczODY1OTMyMC4wLjAuMA..\">la Fabuleuse Cantine</a> pour deux jours riches en d&eacute;couvertes et en rencontres.</p>\n<h3>Programme du Festival</h3>\n<p><strong>Horaires :</strong></p>\n<ul data-spread=\"false\">\n<li>\n<p><strong>Samedi</strong> : 10h00 - 18h30</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Dimanche</strong> : 10h00 - 18h00</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Au programme :</strong></p>\n<ul data-spread=\"false\">\n<li>\n<p>Concerts &amp; animations musicales avec <strong>Hello You</strong> et <strong>La Mani&egrave;re Douce</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>D&eacute;gustations &amp; restauration avec un brunch sp&eacute;cial pour les futurs mari&eacute;s</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>D&eacute;fil&eacute;s de robes &amp; costumes pr&eacute;sent&eacute;s par nos cr&eacute;ateurs partenaires</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Rencontres avec les prestataires : lieux de r&eacute;ception, traiteurs, d&eacute;corateurs, animateurs et bien d\'autres</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Un Magicien Professionnel</h3>\n<p>Parmi les animations, vous pourrez me retrouver sur mon stand ! N\'h&eacute;sitez pas &agrave; venir me voir pour un moment de magie et d&eacute;couvrir mes prestations sp&eacute;ciales pour les mariages.</p>\n<h3>R&eacute;servez Votre Place !</h3>\n<p>Ne manquez pas cette occasion unique de rencontrer les meilleurs prestataires du mariage dans la Loire. Venez &eacute;changer avec eux, d&eacute;couvrir des prestations de qualit&eacute; et profiter d\'un moment convivial au <strong>Festival Esprit Mariage</strong>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.billetweb.fr/festival-esprit-mariage4\">&gt;&gt; R&eacute;servez vos billets d&egrave;s maintenant !</a></p>\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>', '2025-02-04', 'fr', NULL, '2025-02-04 08:36:22', '2025-02-04 10:34:45', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(10, 'Le Délire des Illusions | 2025', 'Yvan Zim présent son spectacle: \"Le Délire des Illusions\" tous les samedi a Lyon', 'lyon-2025-le-delire-des-illusions', 'https://assets.yvanzim.com/images/pages/fringe/yvan-zim-fringe.jpg', '<p>Que se passe t-il lorsqu\'un magicien franco-irlandais se retrouve avec beaucoup de temps libre et un &eacute;go surdimensionn&eacute; ?</p>\n<div id=\"speDescription\">Dans ce nouveau spectacle de 60 minutes, le tricheur, mystificateur et magicien Yvan Zim explore avec humour les nombreuses facettes de la perception de soi.<br /><br />Pr&eacute;parez-vous &agrave; un m&eacute;lange captivant de mentalisme, de com&eacute;die, d\'&eacute;vasions et de magie contemporaine alors qu\'Yvan Zim explore, d&eacute;compose et examine comment l\'on en vient &agrave; se d&eacute;finir au travers des m&eacute;tiers, des passions, des langues et autres faux-semblants...<br /><br />De part son esprit vif, son charme comique et sa dext&eacute;rit&eacute;, Yvan Zim vous tiendra en haleine et vous fera remettre en question le champ des possibles.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><strong>Dates</strong>: Samedi &agrave; 17:00, Fev-Mai 2025<br /><strong>Lieu</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.lerepairedelacomedie.com\">Le Repaire de la Com&eacute;die</a>, <a tabindex=\"0\" href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x47f4eafe7bd3cde7:0xbc6e582dc223efe0?sa=X&amp;ved=1t:8290&amp;ictx=111\" data-url=\"/maps/place//data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x47f4eafe7bd3cde7:0xbc6e582dc223efe0?sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjjj4HNy9iIAxWJQUEAHf_aGPwQ4kB6BAgKEAA\">2 Pl. des Capucins, 69001 Lyon, France</a><br /><strong>Billet</strong>: &euro;15:00</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', '2025-02-05', 'fr', NULL, '2025-02-04 10:35:17', '2025-09-10 14:53:00', 0, 1, NULL, 'Réservations', 'https://www.billetreduc.com/356358/evt.htm', 1),
(11, 'Diner Spectacle Au Marcchiato', 'Diner Spectacle Au Marcchiato ainimé par Yvan Zim.', 'diner-spectacle-11-04-25', 'https://assets.yvanzim.com/images/articles/dinner-show-yvan-zim.png', '<div>\n<p data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"194\">Je me deplace <a href=\"../../fr/magicien-a-vienne\">regulierement a Vienne</a> pour des spectacles de magie. Mais le 11 Avril j\'ai le plaisir d\'animer une soir&eacute;e exceptionnelle au Marchiatto. Un diner spectacle avec au programme : de la magie en close-up pendant le repas, suivie d\'un spectacle in&eacute;dit apr&egrave;s le d&icirc;ner. Une soir&eacute;e inoubliable vous attend !</p>\n</div>\n<div><strong>Dates</strong>: Vendredi 11 Avril 2025 &agrave; 19:30<br /><strong>Lieu</strong>: <a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/d8y7v1vAVPwuZPGy6\">13 place de Miremont, 38200, Vienne</a><br /><strong>Billet</strong>: &euro;20:00</div>\n<div><strong>Reservation</strong>: 09 55 19 22 37</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', '2025-04-11', 'fr', NULL, '2025-02-14 13:28:40', '2025-05-09 13:58:12', 0, 1, NULL, 'Reserver', 'https://www.lemarcchiato.fr/fr/contact-coffee-shop', 1),
(12, '3voutement a la Foire de Saint-Étienne', 'Du 13 au 19 septembre, le trio de magiciens 3nvoûtement sera présent à la Foire de Saint-Étienne en tant qu’exposant.', 'st-etienne-foire-2025', 'https://yvanzim.com/images/temp/foire-st-etienne.png', '<p>Du 13 au 19 septembre, le trio de magiciens <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://3nvoutement.com\">3nvoûtement</a> sera présent à la <strong>Foire de Saint-Étienne</strong> en tant qu’exposant.</p><p>Aux côtés de mes deux partenaires Diego et Maxime nous proposerons des démonstrations mêlant illusion, mentalisme et hypnoses. Ce sera l’occasion de faire découvrir nos divers univers, d’échanger et de partager des instants hors du commun De plus, le thème de cette année est l’Irlande. Ne manquez donc pas l’occasion de rencontrer un véritable Irlandais en personne !</p><p>La Foire de Saint-Étienne est un rendez-vous incontournable, et nous sommes ravis d’y participer pour offrir aux visiteurs une expérience différente, placée sous le signe de la magie et de l’émerveillement.</p><p>Retrouvez toutes les informations pratiques sur le site officiel : <a rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_new\" href=\"https://www.foiredesaintetienne.com\">foiredesaintetienne.com</a></p>', '2025-09-07', 'fr', NULL, '2025-09-07 11:24:51', '2025-09-07 14:18:07', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(13, 'Le Délire des Illusions | Automne 2025', 'Yvan Zim présent son spectacle: \"Le Délire des Illusions\" tous les samedi a Lyon', 'lyon-automne-2025-le-delire-des-illusions', 'https://assets.yvanzim.com/images/pages/fringe/yvan-zim-fringe.jpg', '<p>Et si on faisait connaissance ?<br></p><p>​Faire connaissance, c’est un peu comme assembler un puzzle : chaque information reçue est une pièce qui vient compléter l’image que l’on se fait de l’autre. <br><br>​Dans ce spectacle de 60 minutes, le tricheur, mystificateur et magicien Yvan Zim part à la rencontre du public à travers la magie. Il explore avec humour les nombreuses facettes de ce moment clé : celui où tout commence, celui où l’on découvre l’autre.<br>​Préparez-vous à un mélange captivant de mentalisme, de comédie, d’évasions et de magie contemporaine. Yvan Zim observe, déconstruit et réinvente l’art de faire connaissance, à travers des histoires, des passions… et quelques délires.<br><br>​Par son esprit vif, son charme comique et sa dextérité, Yvan Zim vous tiendra en haleine et vous fera remettre en question le champ des possibles.​</p><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(229, 231, 235); --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgb(59 130 246 / .5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-ro