(25, 11, 'Private parties', '<p> You can book Yvan to perform for a wide range a event such as retirement parties, anniversaries, bachelor & hen parties, family events, festivals, private parties and more. </p>\n            <p> If you are looking for something fun, amazing and different, book Yvan to entertain your guests and make the event unforgettable.</p>', '8', 'https://assets.yvanzim.com/images/shows/private-show.jpg', 'Get In Touch', '/contact', '2023-05-07 18:30:46', '2023-10-14 13:09:26', NULL, 0, 5.00, 5.00, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL),
